# Inception Project Task List

## 1. Environment Setup
- [x] Create a Virtual Machine (VM)
- [x] Configure Ubuntu Server in the VM
- [x] Setup SSH access for easier development
- [x] Configure networking and host resolution (login.42.fr)

## 2. Project Structure
- [x] Create the required directory structure
- [x] Create initial .env file for environment variables
- [x] Create a basic Makefile

## 3. Docker Network
- [x] Define Docker network in docker-compose.yml

## 4. MariaDB Container
- [ ] Create Dockerfile for MariaDB
- [ ] Configure MariaDB (without using built-in image)
- [ ] Create initialization scripts for database and users
- [ ] Configure volume for persistence

## 5. WordPress Container
- [ ] Create Dockerfile for WordPress with php-fpm
- [ ] Configure php-fpm
- [ ] Configure WordPress
- [ ] Configure volume for persistence

## 6. NGINX Container
- [ ] Create Dockerfile for NGINX
- [ ] Generate SSL certificates for TLS
- [ ] Configure NGINX for secure access
- [ ] Setup reverse proxy to WordPress

## 7. docker-compose.yml
- [ ] Configure all services
- [ ] Define volumes
- [ ] Set up networking
- [ ] Configure restart policies

## 8. Makefile
- [x] Create rules for building, starting, and stopping services
- [x] Implement clean-up and reset functionality

## 9. Testing
- [ ] Test entire setup
- [ ] Verify all requirements are met
- [ ] Test automatic restart capability

## 10. Bonus (Optional)
- [ ] Implement Redis cache
- [ ] Set up FTP server
- [ ] Create a static website
- [ ] Set up Adminer
- [ ] Add extra service of choice
